    {
      "id": "2054612657630576902",
      "created_at": "2026-05-13T17:20:05.000Z",
      "text": "The wheels on the bus goes round and round. \nWe'll hear from more physicist with all different conclusions. \nHere's the universe saying to them.\nThe universe doesn't care about what we think. \nWe haven't gotten out their and as a joke we sent the bendover probe .\nAlien Joke 🤣",
      "screen_name": "made_in_ca",
      "name": "riϏϏ forde",
